data.description:
Enjoy the great city of Stillwater, a distant suburb to the twin cities. Quick access to HWY 36, will get you to St Paul in 20 mins, and Minneapolis in half hour. Recently updated, with new appliances, granite counter tops, new or refinished flooring, and a massive 350+ sq ft deck. Enjoy the privacy of the back yard in the summer, with a small garden, and raspberry patch on the property border. The attic features 700+ sq feet of vaulted ceilings, with a 3/4 bath, which would be great for a home office and or gym. The property also has a theater room, which can be quickly set up. Owners suite is nearly 400 sq ft, including the walk in closet and full bath, with Jacuzzi. Stillwater features a ton of historic sights, shopping, and dining, along with plenty of trails for excercise

Tenant is responsible for all utilities, mowing the yard, and shoveling sidewalks. We prefer not to have pets. Looking to do a 12+ month lease
